# Cursor Prompt Templates
## Agentic Performance Testing Framework — IndiaMart
### Phase-by-Phase Prompts + How to Use Them

---

> **How to use this file**
> Each prompt is designed to be pasted directly into Cursor's chat (`Cmd+L` or `Cmd+I`).
> Open the relevant file first, then run the prompt. Cursor will use `.cursor/rules`
> automatically — these prompts build on top of those rules, not replace them.
> Prompts marked **[CHAT]** go in the sidebar chat. Prompts marked **[INLINE]** go
> with `Cmd+I` directly in the file you want to generate.

