## PHASE 2 — Network Simulation + Visual QA

---

### P2-01 · Network simulation agent [CHAT]

```
Create agents/network-sim-agent.ts — Phase 2 network simulation.

This agent wraps the web vitals agent but injects CDP network throttling.

Requirements:
- For each page, run web vitals measurement under ALL 4 network profiles from .cursor/rules
- Use Playwright's CDP session to apply network conditions:
    const client = await context.newCDPSession(page)
    await client.send('Network.emulateNetworkConditions', profile)
- Run the 4 profiles IN PARALLEL (4 Playwright contexts simultaneously)
- Always reset network conditions after each run, even on error — use try/finally
- Return a NetworkSimResult:
    { pageSlug, results: Record<NetworkProfile, VitalsMeasurement | Error> }
- Calculate degradation ratios: e.g. LCP on SLOW_3G / LCP on 4G
- Flag as concerning if LCP degrades > 3x from 4G to SLOW_3G
- The 8-minute timeout applies to the full 4-profile run for one page

Agent function signature:
  runNetworkSimAgent(page: PageConfig, runId: string): Promise<Result<NetworkSimResult>>
```

