## UTILITY PROMPTS — Use at any phase

---

### U-01 · Generate unit tests for any agent [INLINE]

```
Generate a comprehensive unit test file for this agent using Vitest.

Test requirements:
- Mock all external dependencies: Playwright browser, Lighthouse, database, Anthropic SDK
- Test the happy path: valid input → expected Result<T> shape
- Test error handling: what happens when Playwright fails to load the page
- Test the retry logic if this agent has retries
- Test the timeout: mock a slow response and verify the timeout fires
- Test data validation: malformed metric data should return Result error not throw
- Use realistic fixture data based on IndiaMart pages
- Each test should be independent — no shared state between tests
- Aim for > 80% branch coverage on this file
```

